From c4018fef6d948a8a7e0cd1abc59d2cca0f4e361e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Reid Wahl <nrwahl@protonmail.com>
Date: Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:12:23 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 03/26] API: libcrmcluster: Drop enum crm_node_flags and all
 its values

Replace it with an internal enum pcmk__node_status_flags. Also change
pcmk__node_status_t:flags from uint64_t to uint32_t since there are few
values.

This breaks API backward compatibility.

Ref T793

Signed-off-by: Reid Wahl <nrwahl@protonmail.com>
---
 daemons/attrd/attrd_corosync.c         |  4 ++--
 daemons/controld/controld_callbacks.c  |  4 ++--
 daemons/controld/controld_fencing.c    |  6 +++---
 daemons/controld/controld_join_dc.c    |  2 +-
 daemons/controld/controld_membership.c |  4 ++--
 daemons/controld/controld_messages.c   |  3 ++-
 daemons/controld/controld_te_utils.c   |  2 +-
 daemons/fenced/pacemaker-fenced.c      |  2 +-
 include/crm/cluster.h                  | 14 --------------
 include/crm/cluster/internal.h         | 25 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 lib/cluster/membership.c               | 26 ++++++++++++++------------
 11 files changed, 52 insertions(+), 40 deletions(-)

